    <h2 class="w3-center w3-padding-64"><span class="w3-tag w3-wide">ENGLISH COMMUNICATION COURSE DETAILS</span></h2>
    <h4 style="color:Tomato;">We provide English communication training with a 3-level structured curriculum designed to save time and maximize effectiveness.</h4>
    <h7 style="color:blueviolet;">Level 1: PRONUNCIATION AND STRONG COMMUNICATION FOUNDATION</h7>
    <p>Perfect pronunciation of the 44 international phonetic symbols, focusing on correct mouth and tongue movements, as well as airflow control techniques.

      Develop basic communication reflexes through 27 topics related to work and daily life.
      
      Practice communication reflexes through group activities such as debates and discussions.
      
      Achieve an increase of 600+ vocabulary words, 76+ expressive structures, and the ability to communicate effectively on the learned topics.
</p>
    <h7 style="color:blueviolet;">Level 2: PRE-INTERMEDIATE COMMUNICATION
      ACCELERATE REFLEXES</h7>
      <p>Enhance listening and speaking reflexes through 18 specialized topics on work and skills.

        Create a practice environment with 100% native-speaking teachers for listening and speaking. Practice techniques for linking sounds, blending sounds, and intonation.
        
        Practice reflexes through activities such as presentations, debates, arguments, comparisons, etc.
        
        Achieve an increase of 500+ vocabulary words, 68+ expressive structures, and gain confident, fluent, and smooth communication skills.</p>
      <h7 style="color:blueviolet;">Level 3: INTERMEDIATE COMMUNICATION
        NATIVE-LIKE TONE</h7>
      <p>Master listening and speaking skills through 20 specialized topics in commerce and academia.

        Create a practice environment with 100% native-speaking teachers for listening and speaking. Practice techniques for linking sounds, blending sounds, and intonation.
        
        Accelerate speaking speed, practice pronunciation, and native-like intonation.
        
        Achieve an equivalent of 6.5 in IELTS Speaking, and become proficient in communication across various topics.</p>
    <div class="w3-panel w3-leftbar w3-light-grey">
      <p><i>The English communication course at ATENA is divided into classes according to levels including: Elementary, Pre-intermediate, Intermediate and Upper-intermediate. Corresponding to each level, there will be different teaching methods to help students achieve the best results. After the course, students will have paper tests and presentations on topics. We are confident that students will be able to communicate even when studying at the elementary level.</i></p>
